nodes.bodyText:
Does this force the UI to make two calls? If so, I'd rather it be one call where the response is an object - e.g.:
{
  "stepsWithoutEntity": [...],
  "stepsWithEntity": [
    {
      "entityType": "Customer",
      "steps": [...]
    }
  ] 
}

